flow_state|physical_rhythm_social_exchange_creative_movement_deep_focus|balanced|physical_rhythm|social_exchange|creative_movement|deep_focus|Several ways to keep momentum useful|You may find flow through movement, conversation, ideas, or focus depending on the task and setting.|Physical Rhythm appears first, but the other routes are close enough to matter. Some work may need shared pace. Some may need a new angle. Some may need quiet concentration before it is complete. This result is about choosing the condition that turns momentum into useful progress.|active|flow_state::physical_rhythm_social_exchange_creative_movement_deep_focus::balanced
